{"tid":2254289,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"代Post：從男朋友口中得知，今次航空界裁員，純屬政治因素","createTime":"2020-10-22T16:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T07:02:48.000Z","uid":191139,"like":12,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bb44129e533d09bd27d65b5579afd30849102f3a","tid":2254289,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"代post：<br />\n<br />\n今日男友返到屋企，岩岩接佢阿爸再返黎已經話好攰，咁我問佢咩事<br />\n<br />\n原因佢阿爸去左個飯局，途中黎左個某航空界HR第二、三把交椅，叫Albert，佢話今次裁員，係因為早排啲員工搞攬炒搞罷工，再食住武漢肺炎個勢炒左大部份人，有機會想換新血引入支那空中服務員<br />\n<br />\n成程車都係到話炒得好，抵撚死呢啲風涼說話，聽到我男友好攰<br />\n<br />\n個飯局唔多過十個，但個個都係有頭有面嘅有錢佬<br />\n<br />\n想講香港已經唔會再返返去以前，除非打仗，黎一個大翻新"},{"pid":"8d4e6244892407022689a31b5ac9c34d47cbbef4","tid":2254289,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"7d130c66562b65840a4f3c0b9da8911b76e8a000","tid":2254289,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9253406fef1fe621d4eada94dbbc267e313014","tid":2254289,"uid":286897,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6339b1190f4897fadae98ac01896180882d71a15","tid":2254289,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f3f62e92cc109c8fb672c59c78b4a93135c22a1","tid":2254289,"uid":312404,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"零分重作"},{"pid":"7acc443a3994376f72973a93e4aa6d826710ba47","tid":2254289,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟"},{"pid":"724587b758093ca314ee8d65b856c3bcca496574","tid":2254289,"uid":325716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"咁幾時炒埋HA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo